SubjectIssuance of License GL-309 - Woodside Energy Holdings Pty Ltd.
PrecisOrder approving the ISSUANCE OF LICENCE GL-309 to Woodside Energy Holdings Pty Ltd. to export liquefied natural gas from the point on the outlet of the loading arm of a proposed plant to be located in the vicinity of Grassy Point, north of Prince Rupert, British Columbia.
